<lb n="0890a12" ed="T"/>　誐拏尼<note place="inline">十三</note>　誐拏鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>誐尼<note place="inline">十四</note>　誐<g ref="#CB00718">𧹞</g>誐尼
